<p><strong>2020夏日祭盆踊纳凉大会</strong></p>
<p>带你一秒飞回日本</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p3.itc.cn/images01/20200806/249f1187ecc64dc3852eca6f473174c3.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>            <div class="lookall-box">
